summary:
Uh Oh I’m in trouble
part two
title:
Uh Oh I’m in trouble
part two
body:
pairing: Avengers x platonic!oc and eventual Peter Parker x oc

summery: a girl is bored with life at the moment, so what happens when her boredom leads her to meet, and deeply annoy, the worlds mightiest heroes. The Avengers

warnings: swearing , maybe some spelling mistakes

A/N This part is decent  and peter doesn’t come into this until like chapter 4 but btw i do take requests, feel free to send them in

part one 

“Good morning Mr stark, how was your walk?”  A robotic yet human voice awoke me from my ego trance when I arrived at stark towers, also known as the avengers facility. You see Tony wasn’t one for hiding things, meaning it was really easy to waltz into the towers and get a shock from JARVIS.

“it was good, some child got in my way and kept asking for an autograph. Other than that it was great.” I replied in the same low snarky voice as my stark. It wasn’t like I had a choice. My cells had mutated so everything about me was tony stark. “can you tell me where the other Avengers are.”

I was impatient and needed to get this plan going. With my calculations I only had half an hour left until tony woke up and arrived at the tower.

“At the moment all of them are in the living room having breakfast. Would you like me to inform them of your arrival?”  JARVIS being the smol bean that h is gave me all the information that needed to have my fun.

A smirk crossed my face for a brief second. I knew this was going to give me a lifetime of fun.

“No, it’s okay Jarvis I’ll just go surprise them.” You see in my year on the streets there was not much to do, so there may have been a few times that I hacked stark tech and I may or may not have found out the blueprints to the complex. I’ve said it before and I’ll say it till it sinks in, the avengers are idiots.

It didn’t take me long to make it to the living room and it didn’t take me long to put my plan into action.

“Good morning people who don’t pay to live here but still end up eating all my food.” I announce in such an arrogant way I want to puke.

“we save the world, I think we deserve it.” Whoa looks like Mr Hawkeye is an unexpected snarker. Turning myself to look at his relaxed figure on the coach with the one and only black widow/Natasha on the other.

“No need to be like that” I approach him and throw myself onto the empty space next to him. I sit like I own the room, which I technically do (ooooo all the things I would do if I only had time)

“Move it stark.” He reacts like a pro and pushes me away from him, I don’t care I already got what I wanted from him. Time for my next victim.

“Nat are you going to let him talk to me like that.” A pout is prominent on my face as I go to hug her. The hug only lasts a split second before I am pushed away and given a harsh smack.

“Guess that answers my question. Also no fair nat, you know I like it rough.” Ughh I the all these replies. I know that tony stark is a douche and I have to act like him but come on, I hate saying this stuff. It could hurt people’s feelings.

Nat, luckily for me, only sends me the middle finger and I send myself on my way to the next conquest. Mr Thor.

“Sup point break, how’s earth treating you.” Don’t question how I found out his nickname, just know that I was really bored and found stuff that not even bleach can fix.

“Misguard is great, food is great but that nickname that you have given me is still terrible.” Thor smiles like a puppy as I slap his back with laughter. He is such a puppy; I hated having to do what I did.

I waltz my way around the room as I place myself behind my next victim. Mr stars and stripes himself.

“Sup capsicle. Watched any new films lately.” I give him a hug and boii let me just say stars and stripes is the fittest and comfiest ball of muscle around.

Steve Rogers being Steve rogers just gives me a light shove and a laugh, saying “not yet, by the way Bruce and fury are waiting for you in the lab.”

“No one thought to tell me this as I walked in.” This was the perfect opportunity to avoid more conversation so, as I leave the room I set my plan into action. “No one even bothered to say morning even though I said it to you.” I’m throwing my arms up in the air like I’m at an AC/DC concert as I am quickly approaching the door. “I pay for all of this food an..”

I am proud to say that my rant lasted a solid ten minuets. The only reason is stopped was because I had entered the lab and the feeling in that lab was not one of humour.

“Sup Big green and pirate detective. What a surprise to see you two here.” I approach them both and walk around them, pretending I’m making a long journey to face them.

“Stark this is no time for jokes what you discovered last ni..” fury tries to speak to me but my time had run out and I had already accomplished what I came for.

“Sorry fury I would love to stay and chat but I got to unload a huge dump. So hold that thought.” I walk calmly out of the lab not even attempting to listen to fury’s shouts of fury (ayyyy get it) and not even thinking to look back at his winking rage face.

The moments the doors close I’m running to the elevator, you know Starks private one. It doesn’t take me long to go inside and it doesn’t take me long to transform myself into a random women in a shield uniform. The moment the doors open I’m walking out toward the front door.

I couldn’t help but laugh as once I had left the building I smelt and saw a trash covered stark supporting the angriest face I had ever seen. I would have felt like I was walking on clouds however I couldn’t; my pockets were too heavy with the weight of six wallets and two watches.

blog.description: This blog is an automated list of all fic posted on the Archive Of Our Own under the Clint Barton/Natasha Romanov pairing tag. The stories are automatically posted here from the AO3 RSS feed using an IFTTT recipe, but this was made easy thanks to astolat (astolat.tumblr.com). If you would like to set up a similar blog, see the instructions tab :) To check announcements regarding these blogs, go to the tumblr tag #ao3feed announcement. (moderated by enjolbutt.tumblr.com) I hope this blog helps when you are in dire need of feels or a laugh, so enjoy! :)

summary: Tony Stark: Professional Cockblocker
title: Tony Stark: Professional Cockblocker
body:
read it on the AO3 at https://ift.tt/2tgsk6H

by atomic_brunette

Bucky hated Tony. He hated him with everything in his being because goddammit Bucky’d had wanted a nice evening filled with a romantic dinner, romantic dessert, and lots of romantic sex in a room lit by romantic candles and what happened instead?
